# Rust
/target
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock.orig

# Yard runtime state. This repo now self-hosts Yard: we TRACK the shared
# .agents/ policy content (*-policy.yaml, workers.yaml, skills/) and ignore
# per-run operational artifacts AND per-machine state below. The work queue is
# runtime state, not config (82432d8); yardlet.yaml/yard.yaml holds a
# machine-generated workspace identity (workspace_id/created_at) plus personal
# preferences (default_access/max_parallel/auto_ime), so it is per-machine too
# (other repos may choose to track their own).
/.agents/runs/
/.agents/checkpoints/
/.agents/handoffs/
/.agents/telemetry/
/.agents/intents/
/.agents/intent-contract.yaml
/.agents/work-queue.yaml
/.agents/conversations/
/.agents/yardlet.yaml
/.agents/yard.yaml

# Personal / per-machine harness files
*.local
.claude/settings.local.json
.codex/settings.local.json
.claude/worktrees/

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
*.swp
/.agents/worktrees/

# internal planning docs (kept local, not public)
docs/yardlet-final-plan.md
docs/yardlet-roadmap.md
docs/yardlet-queue-ownership-design.md
